Hi,well i wanted to put this a few days ago,but i just couldn't figure it out how to get the links of the songs from box.net x),and today i just found out!,it was so easy : ) and i'm just so stupid x)...

Well here you have,the first fanmix i ever made,it's a fanmix of the couple Jim Halpert & Pam Beesley of the TV series,The Office. Enjoy! and i would like you to comment and tell me what you think!


 
SONGS
1.Waiting for a girl like you-Foreigner (download)

I've been waiting for a girl like you to come into my life
I've been waiting for a girl like you, your loving will survive
I've been waiting for someone new to make me feel alive
Yeah, waiting for a girl like you to come into my life

2.You and Me-Lifehouse (download)

'Cause it's you and me and all of the people with nothing to do
Nothing to lose
And it's you and me and all other people
And i don't know why,i can't keep my eyes off of you 

3.I want you to want me-Cheap trick (download)

I want you to want me
I need you to need me
I'd love you to love me
I'm beggin' you to beg me

4.Iris-Goo goo dolls (download)

And i'd give up forever to touch you
'Cause I know that you feel me somehow
You're the closest to heaven that I'll ever be
And I don't want to go home right now

5.(You want to)Make a memory-Bon Jovi (download) 

Hello again,it's you and me
Kinda always like it used to be
Sippin' wine,killing time
Trying to solve life's mysteries

6.You're beautiful-James Blunt(download) 

You're beautiful.You're beautiful
You're beautiful,It's true
I saw your face in a crowded place,
And I don't know what  to do
'Cause I'll never be with you

7.This i promise you-Nsync (download) 

I'll be your strength
I'll give you hope
Keeping your faith when it's gone
The one you should call
Was standing here all along

8.Happy together-The turtles (download) 

Imagine me and you,I do
I think about you day and night,it's only right
To think about the girl you love and hold her tight
So happy together

9.I don't want to miss a thing-Aerosmith (download) 

I could stay awake just to hear you breathing
Watch you smile while you are sleeping
While you're far away dreaming
I could spend my life in this sweet surrender
I could stay lost in this moment forever
Every moment spent with you is a moment I treasure

10.I wanna hold you-Mcfly (download) 

Tell me that you want me baby,
Tell me that it's true
Tell me that you need me so much more than i need you
Tell me that you're happy honey
Tell me that you're fine
Say you know without me you can't get me of your mind

11.I'm like a lawyer with the way i'm always trying to get you off(me & you)-Fall out boy (download) 

Me and you
Setting in a honeymoon
If i woke up next to you
If i woke up next to you

Hi! Well this is my first time writing in my livejournal,since i created it a long time ago,i hope from now to be more active X)

I just started using Photoshop 7.0 like a week ago and i already got used to it ,since i discovered some cute effects i made my first icon tutorial,and i'm putting it here,so i can share it with you....hope you all like it!


We're going from this...
to this


-Photoshop 7.0
-Selective colors
-Easy steps

Let's start!
1. crop the image you want to use and sharpen if you want.


2.duplicate the base and set it to screen opacity 50%.


3.create a selective color layer(layer>>new layer adjustment>>selective color)
reds:
-100/+44/+90/0
yellows:
-33/+25/0/-37
neutrals:
+25/0/-18/-10



4.duplicate the selective color layer(lower down opacity,it depends on the image you use in this one i put it at 40%).


5.create a new selective color layer:
reds:
-50/-12/0/+20
yellows:
+15/0/-12/0
neutrals:
0/0/-12/-12

Then duplicate the selective color layer.(low down opacity again acording to you image,in this one i used the opacity at 9%)




**optional step)go to layer>>new adjustment layer>>hue/saturation
(add saturation acording to your image and press ok)

6.sharpen,add text if you want or brushes.and it's done.
result:



Other icons using the same effect:


- I would like you to comment if this tutorial helped you.
- Any question about the tutorial,just ask ; )
-I'd totally love to see your results!
